data.name: CheckboxStopIfAwakeUnrecognized.ToolTip
data.value:
Normally, the bot would continue if an awake unrecognized, but if you enable this option it will competely stop.
When missing one or more awakes in the server config, the awakes missing will not be recognized.

data.name: NumericAwakeGroup.ToolTip
data.value:
Awake groups are divided into numbers. This allows to tell the bot that I have 2 or more different group of awakes that I want. The bot will divide the awakes into their own group and stop if any of the awake groups meets their requirement.
In other words, I want one awake (group 1) OR I want another awake (group 2). The bot will stop for either one.
